name: Free The Brow Volumizing & Laminating Brow Gel
about: What it is:An all-in-one clear brow gel and serum that conditions brow hairs while smoothing them into place..Highlighted Ingredients:- Safflower Oil.Ingredient Callouts:It is cruelty-free..What Else You Need to Know:This flake-free formula locks eyebrow hairs in place for up to eight hours with a firm yet flexible hold. It gives brows a laminated effect or smooths them into a perfect arch by using the three-in-one tool designed to deliver more defined, fuller eyebrows..Clinical Results:In a consumer survey of 29 participants, after 3 months of continued use:
ingredients: -Safflower Oil.-Sunflower Oil.-Roselle Hibiscus Sabdariffa..Water (Aqua) (Eau), Ceteareth-30, Propanediol, Glycerin, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate, Polyglyceryl-6 Caprylate, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Carthamus Tinctorius (Safflower) Flower Extract, Hibiscus Sabdariffa Flower Extract, Polyglyceryl-3 Diisostearate, Phenoxyethanol, Potassium Sorbate...The list of ingredients is subject to change, please consult the packaging of the product purchased.
how_to_use: Suggested Usage:.-For a laminated effect, start by brushing Free The Brow through your brows in the opposite direction of hair growth with the spoolie to evenly distribute the product, use comb to separate brow hairs, and then use the brush to flatten and lock them into place to achieve that feathery look. .-For a more shaped look, use the brush edge to shape your brows as desired. Itu2019s super easy to control, so you can achieve the perfect arch. Once youu2019re happy with the shape, Free The Brow locks your brows in place without ever feeling crunchy or flakey throughout the day.  .-Follow up with your favorite brow pencil for added dimension.
